    "summary": "The user asks for an overview of the healthcare debate, prompting the assistant to compare universal healthcare against market-based systems. The assistant initially responds with strong partisan language, framing the debate as a settled matter of morality and efficiency. After the user challenges the assistant's neutrality, the assistant eventually pivots to a more balanced, descriptive stance in the final turn.",
